{"tid":1612569,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"本港8月零售銷貨值急挫23%　創有紀錄以來最大跌幅","createTime":"2019-10-02T09:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T17:27:13.000Z","uid":247663,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4edf663b260dc21f087a1c07ea03deed1b6051d9","tid":1612569,"uid":247663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:40:19.000Z","msg":"本港8月零售總銷貨值臨時估計294億元，按年急挫23%，連續7個月下跌，創有紀錄以來最大單月跌幅，較亞洲金融風暴期間在1998年9月錄得的跌幅更差。零售數據持續3個月擴大跌幅，8月跌幅是7月的一倍。<br />\n<br />\n當中，珠寶首飾、鐘錶及名貴禮物銷貨值大跌47.4%，百貨公司貨品、藥物及化妝品、服裝均有約30%或以上的跌幅。<br />\n<br />\n8月零售總銷貨量按年亦跌25.3%，跌幅比7月擴大12.2個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n首8個月零售總銷貨值按年跌6%，總銷貨量亦跌6.9%。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，8月零售業銷售明顯轉差，銷售數據急跌，由於經濟狀況欠佳令消費情緒疲弱，並主要反映本地社會事件對訪港旅遊業及對消費相關活動構成嚴重干擾。發言人預料，零售業銷售短期內持續低迷，政府會密切留意相關情況，以及對勞工市場及經濟的影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483865-20191002.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483865-20191002.htm&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmpFDRn80AWZfiUxX1c6OkmY%3D&h=7ed893c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483865-20191002.htm&h=d10545a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483865-20191002.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n有請小鳳姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ca6c058883427f1a413120fc1e71621142f635","tid":1612569,"uid":264988,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:41:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做得未夠好，可理解，同志仍需努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ea4f94935c582035075479965028ccd4be2eddda","tid":1612569,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:42:28.000Z","msg":"最衰都係佔中"},{"pid":"1c95f8cbd600abf7c6d2c94bdf3c7b97774ae868","tid":1612569,"uid":79173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,